				<td class="left-col">reed.co.ukFreecruitmentAuth</td>
				<td class="right-col">Keeps you signed in to your account, once you've signed in to reed.co.uk/recruiter</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="left-col">reed.utmx</td>
				<td class="right-col">Contains information used for testing new journeys and features</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="left-col">NewJobsSinceTime</td>
				<td class="right-col">Remembers the last time a user ran a search so we can show jobs they haven't seen before</td>
			</tr>
